      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "2 Chronicles 33:6",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", where mention is made of the place where it was done, the valley of the son of Hinnom: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "and observed times; lucky or unlucky, which was judged of by omens, and by the position of the stars: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "and used enchantments, and dealt with familiar spirits and wizards; to get knowledge of things to come; all which are forbid and condemned by the law of Moses; see Deuteronomy 18:10, ",
        "children": [
