        "text": "pass through the fire",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "] See note on ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "2 Kings 16:3",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". ‘The valley of the son of Hinnom’ mentioned by the Chronicler was a ravine on the south and west of Jerusalem, the south-east extremity of which had the name of ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
