        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". Because of the horrors which had been perpetrated there, the place was defiled, and converted into a receptacle of all that was foul and offensive, for the destruction of which constant fires were kept burning. For this reason the name ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Ge Hinnom",
        "children": []
      },
