        "text": "practised augury",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". The rendering of A.V. is from the Vulgate, but that version in other places represents the sense as being ‘to use augury’. (See Vulg. of ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
